<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>明 · 色釉 - 瓷韵中华</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ma+Shan+Zheng&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/ming.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div id="cursor"></div>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <header class="hero-section" data-cursor="VIEW">
        <div class="ink-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-title">
                <!-- <div class="royal-seal">御赐</div> -->
                <span>明</span> <span>·</span> <span>色</span> <span>釉</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-subtitle">皇 家 典 范 · 千 窑 一 宝</div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="alchemy-section">
        <div class="section-header reveal-up">
            <h2>五 色 · 天 成</h2>
            <p>THE ART OF MONOCHROME GLAZE</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">
            <div class="color-card-wrapper" style="flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 40px;">
                
                <div class="color-card reveal-up">
                    <div class="color-sample sample-red" data-cursor="FIRE">
                        <div class="glaze-process">
                            <div><i class="bi bi-fire mb-2 fs-3"></i><br>氧化铜<br>还原焰</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="brand-font">祭红</h3>
                    <div class="chem-formula">Copper Red</div>
                    <p class="text-muted mt-3 small">"千窑一宝"，色泽深沉安定，不流釉，不脱口，如红宝石般珍贵，专用于皇家祭日。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="color-card reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                    <div class="color-sample sample-white" data-cursor="TOUCH">
                        <div class="glaze-process" style="color:#333; background: #eee;">
                            <div><i class="bi bi-droplet mb-2 fs-3"></i><br>脱胎<br>暗刻</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="brand-font">甜白</h3>
                    <div class="chem-formula">Sweet White</div>
                    <p class="text-muted mt-3 small">永乐创烧。釉层洁白莹润，如白糖一般，给人以甜润之感，常配以暗刻龙纹。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="color-card reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="color-sample sample-yellow" data-cursor="ROYAL">
                        <div class="glaze-process" style="color:#333; background: #eccc68;">
                            <div><i class="bi bi-star mb-2 fs-3"></i><br>铁黄<br>低温</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="brand-font">娇黄</h3>
                    <div class="chem-formula">Imperial Yellow</div>
                    <p class="text-muted mt-3 small">弘治达到顶峰。色泽娇嫩如鸡油，是帝王专属的至尊之色，庶民禁用。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="color-card reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                    <div class="color-sample sample-blue" data-cursor="SKY">
                        <div class="glaze-process">
                            <div><i class="bi bi-cloud mb-2 fs-3"></i><br>氧化钴<br>高温</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="brand-font">霁蓝</h3>
                    <div class="chem-formula">Sacrificial Blue</div>
                    <p class="text-muted mt-3 small">宣德时期名品。色泽深沉如蓝宝石，釉面不流不裂，主要用于祭天大典。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="color-card reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="color-sample sample-green" data-cursor="JADE">
                        <div class="glaze-process">
                            <div><i class="bi bi-tree mb-2 fs-3"></i><br>氧化铁<br>还原焰</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="brand-font">冬青</h3>
                    <div class="chem-formula">Winter Green</div>
                    <p class="text-muted mt-3 small">仿龙泉窑青釉。永乐时期烧制最精，釉色苍翠，肥厚如脂，有如美玉。</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline-section">
        <div class="section-header reveal-up">
            <h2>发展脉络</h2>
            <p>DEVELOPMENT TRACK</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline">

            <div class="timeline-item left reveal-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>永乐甜白釉</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">因永乐帝尚白崇礼，御窑承命精研。创“厚釉薄胎”之法，成色莹润暖白，如脂若玉。由此确立单色釉为皇家礼器之正统，开一代美学先河。</p>
                    <img src="/media/china/明色釉甜白釉.png">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item right reveal-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>永乐、宣德红釉</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">为祭祀礼制之需，窑工以铜入釉，经烈火反复试炼。终得色沉似血、宝光内敛之祭红，成就“千窑一宝”传奇，彰显庙堂庄严。</p>
                    <img src="/media/china/明色釉.png">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item left reveal-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>宣德、嘉靖蓝釉</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">承祭祀礼制而发展，尤以祭天为重。霁蓝釉色邃如深海，匀净肃穆，专饰礼器。其色即是对苍穹与神灵的具象凝铸。</p>
                    <img src="/media/china/明蓝釉.png">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item right reveal-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>弘治黄釉</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">因“黄为至尊”礼制，御窑专供帝王。技艺臻于极致，釉色娇嫩纯正如鸡油，成为皇权视觉象征，制度色彩达至顶峰。</p>
                    <img src="/media/china/明弘治黄釉.png">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item left reveal-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>正德孔雀绿</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted">随晚明世俗审美与贸易交流而兴。借鉴异域技法，创低温二次烧成之翠绿釉，色泽艳丽夺目，标志色釉由礼器转向陈设玩赏。</p>
                    <img src="/media/china/明孔雀绿.png">
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="micro-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header reveal-up">
                <h2>微 观 · 橘 皮 纹</h2>
                <p>ORANGE PEEL TEXTURE</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-12 text-center reveal-up">
                    <div class="micro-wrapper" id="microScope">
                        <img src="/media/china/明红釉.png" class="micro-img" alt="Details">
                        <div class="micro-hint"><i class="bi bi-zoom-in"></i> 探索釉面气泡</div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-muted" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        宣德祭红釉面往往高低不平，呈橘皮状，俗称“橘皮纹”。这是由于釉料在高温下气泡破裂又重新愈合形成的独特肌理。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/common.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/ming.js"></script>
</body>
</html>